{
  "stem": "26731.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By the gates of Berlin, the Russians will meet their defeat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The siege, I would say, it was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] probably a week-- you still had the gun, but really, bombardment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people tell us, you are very fortunate that the Russians took Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Americans would just have pulled back and really bombarded it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there you had house-to-house fighting, see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he saw, remember, out going for water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a group of Mongolian transcripts, Russian, we were running.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you think could have happened-- will have happened after the Russians caught him?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were the troops from General [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a Russian general who fought for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could see the brigade-- or whether they called it, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That-- I still remember this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not see that exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I assure you, at the time the Russians came, they took off their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the reason why they asked me, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Come, come, come, come, come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- all Jews kaput.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are not-- you are just a soldier or a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, prove it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Thanks goodness I had my-- they knew enough probably that-- actually, there was some German speaking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was amazing, probably deliberately, the front lines by some warrior Germans, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me see, anything important.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
